These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-6-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: dutch, brazilian, spanish, indian, egyptian, turkish, pakistani
7 different pets are kept: rabbit, pony, lizard, snake, hamster, fish, guinea-pig
 1. the dutch is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5
 2. the spanish is somewhere to the right of the dutch##5
 3. the pakistani is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is in an odd position##4
 5. the brazilian is somewhere to the right of the dutch##5
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the indian##1
 7. the brazilian is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the pakistani is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the owner of the pony is on the far left or far right##3
10. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the left of the turkish##5
11. the turkish is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
12. the egyptian is on the left of the turkish##1
13. the turkish is in the middle##1
14. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the spanish##5
15. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5
16. the owner of the hamster is not the pakistani##6
17. the dutch is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
18. the owner of the pony is not the spanish##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7      |
| Nationality   | dutch | indian | egyptian | turkish | pakistani | spanish | brazilian |
| Pet           | snake   | fish    | guinea-pig       | rabbit     | lizard    | hamster   | pony |

