 4. the fan folk is on the left of the italian##1
 5. the italian is somewhere to the left of the polish##5
 6. the mexican is somewhere to the left of the italian##5
 7. the spanish is on the left of the mexican##1
 8. the brazilian is on the left or right of the fan jazz##3
 9. the fan gospel is somewhere to the right of the fan punk##5
10. the mexican is on the right of the fan rock##1
11. the fan rock is not the italian##6
12. the fan jazz is on the far right##1
13. the fan rock is somewhere to the left of the fan punk##5
14. the fan folk is the british##1
15. the mexican is on the left of the fan folk##1
16. the fan gospel is somewhere to the right of the indian##5
17. the italian is on the right of the fan folk##1
18. the fan folk is somewhere to the left of the fan punk##5
19. the fan punk is on the right of the fan indie##1
20. the fan ambient is on the right of the fan rock##1
21. the fan ambient is somewhere to the left of the british##5

