 1. the coach is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who's sport is parkour is in an odd position##4
 3. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
 4. the paramedic is not the person who's sport is parkour##6
 5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in the middle##1
 6. the architect is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
 7. the firefighter is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the firefighter is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is sailing##5
 9. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere to the left of the bartender##5
10. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not the bartender##6
11. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the left of the coach##5
12. the paramedic is in an even position##4
13. the person who's sport is sailing is not the accountant##6
14. the person who's sport is climbing is between the person who's sport is sailing and the firefighter##2
15. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
16. the paramedic is on the left of the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
