 5. the person eating cranberry is somewhere to the left of the person eating plum##5
 6. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the right of the person eating eggplant##5
 7. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
 8. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 9. the person driving the train is on the left of the person eating radish##1
10. the person driving the train is in the middle##1
11. the person eating orange is on the far right##1
12. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
13. the person driving the scooter is not the person eating lemon##6
14. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the right of the person driving the trike##5
15. the person eating plum is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
16. the person driving the trike is on the far left or far right##3
17. the person eating lime is somewhere to the right of the person eating eggplant##5
18. the person eating cranberry is not the person driving the tram##6
19. the person eating cranberry is between the person eating eggplant and the person driving the roller##2
