 5. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 6. the owner of the rat is not the person driving the subway##6
 7. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the dog##5
 8. the person driving the bike is the owner of the horse##1
 9. the owner of the dog is not the person driving the roller##6
10. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
11. the owner of the cat is the person driving the bus##1
12. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5
13. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5
14. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
15. the owner of the rabbit is not the person driving the bike##6
16. the person driving the bus is on the far left or far right##3
