.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-6-16::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  firefighter, paramedic, engineer, dressmaker, photographer, pilot, software-developer
There are 7 different nationalities: mexican, thai, dutch, indonesian, spanish, german, japanese
 1. the firefighter is somewhere to the left of the thai##5
 2. the dutch is somewhere to the left of the software-developer##5
 3. the japanese is not the engineer##6
 4. the software-developer is on the left or right of the photographer##3
 5. the dressmaker is on the left of the firefighter##1
 6. the mexican is on the far right##1
 7. the engineer is on the left or right of the japanese##3
 8. the engineer is between the thai and the japanese##2
 9. the dutch is in an even position##4
10. the spanish is somewhere to the right of the software-developer##5
11. the spanish is between the pilot and the software-developer##2
12. the thai is on the left or right of the dutch##3
13. the dressmaker is somewhere to the left of the photographer##5
14. the thai is the software-developer##1
15. the photographer is somewhere to the right of the japanese##5
16. the paramedic is on the right of the indonesian##1
17. the firefighter is on the right of the dressmaker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |     4      |      5       |    6    |       7        |
| Job           | dressmaker    | firefighter     | paramedic | engineer | software-developer | photographer | pilot |
| Nationality   | german | indonesian | japanese     | dutch   | thai      | spanish  | mexican      |

