.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-6-17::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: fanta, tea, water, milk, coffee, sprite, lemonade
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: swimming, tennis, handball, basketball, rowing, weightlifting, skiing
 1. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person drinking coffee##5
 2. the person drinking coffee is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 3. the person who's sport is handball is on the far left##1
 4. the person drinking milk is not the person who's sport is basketball##6
 5. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
 6. the person drinking coffee is between the person drinking lemonade and the person drinking milk##2
 7. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
 8. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 9. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking water and the person drinking lemonade##2
10. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
11. the person drinking milk is not the person who's sport is skiing##6
12. the person drinking lemonade is in an even position##4
13. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is skiing##5
14. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not the person drinking coffee##6
15. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2       |    3     |    4    |     5      |  6   |    7     |
| Beverage   | tea | milk | coffee | lemonade | sprite      | water | fanta      |
| Sport      | handball    | weightlifting | tennis | rowing   | skiing | basketball | swimming |

