.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-6-18::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: sprite, lemonade, soy-milk, coffee, cola, water, fanta
There 7 different types of food: kiwi, orange, grapes, broccoli, lemon, watermelon, grapefruit
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person eating lemon##3
 3. the person eating kiwi is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
 4. the person eating broccoli is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
 5. the person eating orange is somewhere to the right of the person eating lemon##5
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person eating orange##1
 7. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 8. the person eating grapefruit is not the person drinking soy-milk##6
 9. the person eating grapefruit is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
10. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
11. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5
12. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking water##1
13. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
14. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person eating kiwi##3
15. the person eating broccoli is somewhere to the left of the person eating orange##5
16. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
17. the person eating broccoli is in an odd position##4
18. the person drinking sprite is not the person eating broccoli##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |       2       |     3     |  4   |    5    |    6     |      7      |
| Beverage   | cola  | soy-milk | fanta       | water | sprite     | coffee | lemonade |
| Food       | lemon | grapes         | broccoli | orange | watermelon | kiwi  | grapefruit      |

