.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-6-19::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  writer, analyst, firefighter, security-guard, lawyer, software-developer, nurse
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: soccer, cycling, weightlifting, climbing, snowboarding, rowing, lacrosse
 1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the nurse and the person who's sport is soccer##2
 2. the firefighter is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 3. the nurse is not the person who's sport is climbing##6
 4. the analyst is the person who's sport is soccer##1
 5. the firefighter is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##5
 6. the security-guard is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the software-developer is somewhere to the left of the lawyer##5
 9. the nurse is somewhere to the right of the firefighter##5
10. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is climbing##5
11. the nurse is somewhere to the left of the lawyer##5
12. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left or right of the nurse##3
13. the security-guard is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rowing##5
14. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
15. the person who's sport is rowing is not the lawyer##6
16. the software-developer is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
17. the person who's sport is cycling is not the software-developer##6
18. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cycling##5
19. the analyst is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
20. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
21. the lawyer is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
22. the security-guard is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |   2    |    3    |     4      |       5       |     6      |     7     |
| Job     | analyst     | firefighter | nurse | security-guard | software-developer | lawyer   | writer |
| Sport   | soccer | lacrosse | weightlifting | climbing | snowboarding         | cycling | rowing   |

