.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-6-20::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: tea, almond-milk, soy-milk, fanta, milk, sprite, juice
The people have 7 different hobbies: filmmaking, magic-tricks, drawing, chess, baking, hiking, writing
 1. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
 2. the person who's hobby is writing is not the person drinking sprite##6
 3. the person drinking tea is between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person drinking almond-milk##2
 4. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##5
 5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is baking##5
 7. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5
 8. the person drinking milk is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5
10. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
11. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
12. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
13. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3    |    4    |    5     |      6      |    7    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | juice   | almond-milk  | tea     | milk | fanta    | sprite |
| Hobby      | hiking     | chess | drawing | baking | filmmaking  | writing | magic-tricks |

 